//! Browser Bridge and safe web tools.
//!
//! The bridge deliberately keeps the browser connection local.  A pairing token is generated by
//! Papyrus, the extension has to opt in to the current tab, and every action carries a page
//! revision.  The implementation is intentionally small enough to audit: the browser never
//! receives filesystem paths, cookies, storage values, or arbitrary JavaScript.

